overview.en: MoneroV fulfills the long overdue desire for a truly anonymous, decentralized, finite peer-to-peer electronic currency. Individuals and businesses can transact securely, reliably and anonymously with low fees using MoneroV.
overview.zh: MoneroV满足了人们长期对于真正的匿名、去中心化、有限的点对点电子货币的需求。 个人和企业可通过MoneroV以低廉的费用安全、可靠和匿名地进行交易。
